The paper discusses the application of declarative programming in data analytics, which is a topic that falls under the database (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the development of systems and optimization techniques, which are topics that fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed computing (cs.DC) sub-categories. Finally, the paper proposes declarative languages for expressing data analysis tasks, which is a topic that falls under programming languages (cs.PL) sub-category.
